The analysis of the same sample after NH4OH is presented in Fig. 2(e–g). The surface looks cleaner and many of the “small grains” have disappeared. This observation is not limited to the image presented here but rather general. We observe a clear facet depending CPD contrast and the number of GBs that exhibit upward band-bending is reduced. The median value ΔΘ~GB\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
